body_html:
Hello everyone, I have the same mistake, but it holds with python 3.
So I try these codes:

pip3 uninstall "tensorflow==1.7.*"
before reinstall

pip3 install --upgrade "tensorflow==1.7.*"

It worked for me,

body:
Hello everyone, I have the same mistake, but it holds with python 3. 
So I try these codes:

`pip3 uninstall "tensorflow==1.7.*"`
before reinstall

```
pip3 install --upgrade "tensorflow==1.7.*"
```

It worked for me,
